1104
01:29:29,521 --> 01:29:31,159
¡Encantador su pueblo!

1105
01:29:31,641 --> 01:29:33,233
¡Este pueblo es encantador!

1106
01:29:34,081 --> 01:29:34,957
Gracias.

1107
01:29:37,161 --> 01:29:38,276
¡Ese es mi marido!

1108
01:29:39,681 --> 01:29:40,909
¡Comete usted un grave error!

1109
01:29:44,481 --> 01:29:46,551
Napoloni no debe invadir
Osterlich.

1110
01:29:46,721 --> 01:29:47,915
